{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotations","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"array must conform to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations in the array.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations